lead_paragraph: Sophie Brunner's three-point play with 1.9 seconds left gave No. 8 Arizona State a 69-68 victory over short-handed Southern California on Sunday, keeping the Sun Devils tied atop the Pac-12.

headline.print_headline: Brunner's 3-Point Play Lets No. 8 Arizona State Escape USC
